snippet.title: Warp 1 for the BBC Micro
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

A strategy game with partially action. Warp 1 is based on Star Trek but it is not an official Star Trek game.

The captain of the Enterprise has been gone missing and you have to find him. You took over the Enterprise and now have to warp through various sectors and eventually fight Klingons.

Was later rereleased as Trek II.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yMcvXTQZ894
